    "title": {
      "rendered": "8 Grant Research Tools for Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>According to the <a href=\"https://www.resilia.com/blog/highlights-from-the-giving-usa-foundation-2022-report\">Giving USA 2022 Report</a>, giving by foundations to nonprofit organizations grew by 3.4% in 2021 to $90.88 billion. Foundation grants now represent 19% of total giving to nonprofits \u2013 the largest share on record.</p>\n<p>The websites listed below can help your nonprofit search and apply for grant funding. If you need training in grant writing, a good place to start is with this free <a href=\"https://learning.candid.org/training/courses/introduction-to-proposal-writing/\">Introduction to Proposal Writing course</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.learngrantwriting.org/learn-grant-writing-book/\">best-selling book, <em>How to Write a Grant</em></a>.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">1. Candid :: <a href=\"https://candid.org/find-funding\">candid.org/find-funding</a></h2>\n<p>Candid offers a searchable database of foundations and grants, grants for individuals, and Requests for Proposals published by funders.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://candid.org/find-funding\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-33966 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Candid.org_.jpg?resize=800%2C527\" alt=\"Screenshot of Candid.org Homepage - a grantseeking tool.\" width=\"800\" height=\"527\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Candid.org_.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Candid.org_.jpg?resize=300%2C198&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Candid.org_.jpg?resize=768%2C506&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Candid.org_.jpg?resize=50%2C33&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://fconline.foundationcenter.org/?_gl=1*11wk0n6*_gcl_aw*R0NMLjE2NjI4MzUyOTEuQ2owS0NRanc2X0NZQmhEakFSSXNBQm51U3pwVWVnMS1GV0I1NWVsazdlZDY4ZWxvQUVkZERTcjF0RVRtNVI0S3c3aldWblh6Wm1UcnJRMGFBdkxSRUFMd193Y0I.*_ga*MjcwMTM3OTkzLjE2NjI4MzUyOTE.*_ga_5W8PXYYGBX*MTY2MjgzNTI5MC4xLjEuMTY2MjgzNjA2Mi42MC4wLjA.&amp;_ga=2.253061903.78417726.1662835291-270137993.1662835291&amp;_gac=1.224850408.1662835291.Cj0KCQjw6_CYBhDjARIsABnuSzpUeg1-FWB55elk7ed68eloAEddDSr1tETm5R4Kw7jWVnXzZmTrrQ0aAvLREALw_wcB\">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>2. Devex :: <a href=\"https://pgs.devex.com/devex-pro-funding/\">devex.com/funding</a></h2>\n<p>Devex features international funding opportunities from 850+ sources including USAID, World Bank, the European Union, and the Bill &amp; Melinda Gates Foundation.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://pgs.devex.com/devex-pro-funding/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34034 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/DEVEX-Pro-Funding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=800%2C533\" alt=\"Screenshot of devex.com Homepage - a funding tool for international development organizations.\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/DEVEX-Pro-Funding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/DEVEX-Pro-Funding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/DEVEX-Pro-Funding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/DEVEX-Pro-Funding-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=50%2C33&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://pgs.devex.com/devex-pro-funding-orgs/#pricing-anchor\">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">3. Grant Gopher :: <a href=\"https://grantgopher.com/\">grantgopher.com</a></h2>\n<p>Grant Gopher is a simple and powerful grant research database that nonprofits can search by state, county, program, and keywords.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://grantgopher.com/#/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-33964 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Grant-Gopher-Homepage.jpg?resize=800%2C493\" alt=\"Screenshot of grantgopher.org Homepage - a grantseeking tool for schools, nonprofits, and municipalities.\" width=\"800\" height=\"493\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Grant-Gopher-Homepage.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Grant-Gopher-Homepage.jpg?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Grant-Gopher-Homepage.jpg?resize=768%2C473&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Grant-Gopher-Homepage.jpg?resize=50%2C31&amp;ssl=1 50w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Grant-Gopher-Homepage.jpg?resize=324%2C200&amp;ssl=1 324w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://grantgopher.com/Plans-Pricing\">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>4. Grants.gov :: <a href=\"https://www.grants.gov/\">grants.gov</a></h2>\n<p>Grants.gov enables grant seekers to search for federal grants offered by the U.S. Government.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.grants.gov/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34030 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Grants.gov-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=800%2C536\" alt=\"Screenshot of grants.gov Homepage - a grantseeking tool for federal grants.\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Grants.gov-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Grants.gov-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C201&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Grants.gov-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C515&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Grants.gov-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=50%2C34&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Our <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Certificate in Social Media Marketing &amp; Fundraising</a> program covers the fundamentals of social media marketing and fundraising for your nonprofit. Participants will learn how to create a social media strategy, how to craft a content marketing plan, and current best practices for using social media for community engagement and fundraising.</p>\n<p>The program requires the completion of three webinars and costs $100 USD. To earn the 2024 certificate, you can attend the webinars live or view the recordings \u2013 or a combination of both. <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Learn more &amp; register</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-37646 size-full aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=960%2C755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C604&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Social-Media-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C39&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>5. GrantScape :: <a href=\"https://www.thegrantscape.com/\">thegrantscape.com</a></h2>\n<p>GrantScape is a database of current grant opportunities offered by foundations and federal, state, and local governments.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.thegrantscape.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-34031\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantScape-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=800%2C571\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"571\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantScape-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantScape-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C214&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantScape-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C548&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantScape-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=50%2C36&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.thegrantscape.com/subscribe.aspx\">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>6. GrantStation :: <a href=\"https://grantstation.com/\">grantstation.com</a></h2>\n<p>GrantStation offers a variety of grant writing tools (in addition to their database of funding opportunities) to help nonprofits secure grant awards.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://grantstation.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-34037\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantStation-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=800%2C469\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantStation-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantStation-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantStation-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C450&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantStation-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=50%2C29&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://grantstation.com/product/purchase-grantstation-membership\">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>7. GrantWatch :: <a href=\"https://www.grantwatch.com/\">grantwatch.com</a></h2>\n<p>GrantWatch allows users to filter searches by interest, location, funding source, keyword and/or Grant ID#.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.grantwatch.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-34038\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantWatch-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=800%2C547\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"547\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantWatch-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantWatch-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C205&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantWatch-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C525&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/GrantWatch-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=50%2C34&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.grantwatch.com/plans.php\">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2><strong>8. Instrumentl :: <a href=\"https://www.instrumentl.com/\">instrumentl.com</a></strong></h2>\n<p>Instrumental is an online database of grant opportunities that matches nonprofits with the right funders and then enables nonprofits to efficiently track and manage their grants.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.instrumentl.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-34039\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Instrumental-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=800%2C503\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"503\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Instrumental-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Instrumental-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C189&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Instrumental-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C483&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Instrumental-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=50%2C31&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.instrumentl.com/pricing\">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></p>\n<p>In addition, for those nonprofits located in the United States, you can check with <a href=\"https://www.unitedphilforum.org/find-your-regional-philanthropy-serving-organization\">regional philanthropy-serving organizations</a>\u00a0and your <a href=\"https://www.councilofnonprofits.org/find-your-state-association\">state association of nonprofits</a>.</p>\n<hr />\n<div style=\"background-color: #8362ae; padding: 4px;\"></div>\n<div style=\"background-color: #efebeb; padding: 5px;\">\n<h2><strong> \u25ba </strong><b>About the Author</b></h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background-color: #efebeb; padding: 5px;\"><a style=\"color: #8362ae;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a> is the founder and editor-in-chief of Nonprofit Tech for Good. Fueled by a strong passion for the Internet, Heather spends her days (and some nights) helping nonprofits, charities, and NGOs worldwide utilize the internet as a tool for social good.</div>\n<hr />\n",
